Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  粉丝同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, fellow fanatics
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看派斯精选
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Patchy's Pick
