Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come on back to the galley?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.85,0:01:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天在给你们整点消遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cooking up a real treat for you today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118,512)}骗上贼船
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来看我最爱的节目  骗上贼船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to see me favorite show, Shanghaied
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boring
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不就是我的没意思小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't my less than amusing sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鹦鹉波蒂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty the Parrot?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  跟观众们打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, say hello to the nice people
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是被强行关押在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm being held here against my will
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.67,0:01:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.32,0:01:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.05,0:01:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
