Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You in there, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.20,0:01:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去  你个坏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here, you scurvy bird
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  播动画片
