Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天从我麦片盒里生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby from my cereal box
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个不是小孩  是大锚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a baby, that's a giant anchor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说该给人家起什么名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think we should name it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们两个去爬锚绳去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two go climb its anchor rope?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它一定会通往很远的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it goes somewhere far away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我们干的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't do it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可清白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our hands are clean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要刨根问底查个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to get to the bottom of this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是问顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be the top?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几英寸后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ship
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.15,0:03:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你到底要胡思乱想多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, how long are you going to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your little fantasy world?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, look
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有大船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a giant ship
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于能给这乱扔大锚的来一点教训了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can finally give this anchor-dropper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a piece of my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不太好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那艘船周围有可怕的绿光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ship has a spooky green glow around it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能就是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's probably because
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船主实在是游手好闲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,its good-for-nothing owner is too lazy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懒得打扫  锚也不好好放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clean or drop his anchors in the right place
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是这木头箱子的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who owns this crate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(645.907,633.467)}主人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要投诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to file a complaint
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方是不是感觉很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this place seem familiar?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉就是有那么点印象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it just kind of ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(976.368,920)}响 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道谁是这船的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who owns this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是想不起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't place the name
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,499.479)}飞天魔鬼所有
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  名字不叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这船是红男爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ship belongs to the Red Baron
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.64,0:04:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁胆敢在飞天魔鬼的地盘打扰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who be disturbing the Flying Dutchman in his own lair?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要投诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants to complain to you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可可可没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I-I-I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.73,0:05:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你骂人家船脏人懒又是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what about all that stuff about him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,having a dirty ship and being lazy and all?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I never said that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,侮辱一个人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Insulting a man's ship
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比侮辱一个人的妈更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be worse than insulting his mother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚骂的是他妈脏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was his mother you said was dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是船脏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not his ship
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're next
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是差一点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是差一点点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a closer one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们两个怎么每次捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How come when they act up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都要欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all they get is the welcome wagon?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我说  早就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你们要不要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you going to try that again?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  他们不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, they're not
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1063.999,681.842)}鬼矩手册
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论是谁登上了飞天魔鬼的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Whosoever sets foot on the Flying Dutchman's ship
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是不是不请自来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"uninvited or otherwise
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都要成为他的鬼水手  一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"shall become members of his ghostly crew forever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.35,0:06:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会领名片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will we be getting business cards?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们现在是我的鬼水手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're part of my crew now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.85,0:06:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的工作就是四处航行吓唬别人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and our job is to sail around and frighten people
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会很累人  麻木人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt'll be grueling, mind-numbing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还反反复复的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and repetitive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.23,0:06:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多就像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白天的电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,daytime television
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你给我听好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you listen here, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是真觉得我会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm going to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这垃圾堆里待个五分钟以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spend more than five minutes on this dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you're crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒是看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁教你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever told you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把油灯放硬木板边上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that hanging oil lamps
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to hardwood paneling was a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要给我看东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're going to show me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, that's very nice
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意  魔术表演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this, some kind of magic act?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.02,0:07:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还要进去飞天绝望里玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would anyone else like to enter the Fly of Despair?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们明白自己地位了  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we know our place now, Mr. Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会照你说的做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll do anything you say
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么你们俩新来的可以  擦甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then for starters, you can swab the deck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活生生的鬼拖把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a real, live ghost mop
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有这顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got this hat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今晚要去裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're heading down to Bikini Bottom tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来闹个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a little haunting spree
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要这艘船的外观非常吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I want this ship to look good and scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说你要船的外观非常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you want it to look good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也许可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we could probably
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人家说的是要外观特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he means he wants it to look so good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好到可怕的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it's scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者可能是让船的外观很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe that by looking so scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以忽略掉船很难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you forget that it doesn't look good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.32,0:07:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It simply means
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管什么意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind what it means
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子吓人就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want it to look scary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天花板发霉  水池里有虫爬的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mold growing on the ceilings, bugs in the sink
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你不要船好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you don't want it to look good?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get moving
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手的命儿真是妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sailor's life is a wonderful life
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,命儿实在妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wonderful life for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚夜色真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a night be this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手们  跟我嚎叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crew, howl with me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让七大洋颤栗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so that we might set the seven seas ablaze with fear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  方家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, square one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然粉家伙在负责航行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since pink one's working the navigation
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让你来找我们第一个受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's up to you to find our first victim
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  用这把望远镜找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, use this spyglass
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间不等人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're burning moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看能找到谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see who we can find
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长  那边那位可以吓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain, there's a guy we can scare
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有四块饼干  吃掉了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had four biscuits, and I ate one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有三块了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I only had three
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.36,0:09:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到有小孩子夜不归宿让我开心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It does me heart good to see children out after dark
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉家伙  给我们带到石头后边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink one, take us behind those rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到石头后边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moving behind the rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会把划痕弄干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll buff out those scratches
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  那个别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, never mind it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给暗号你们就跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just jump out when I give the signal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be burdened
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.07,0:09:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我的鬼海盗们留下挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the haunting memory of my ghostly ghost pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暗号就那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that the signal?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.87,0:10:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我的鬼海盗们留下挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the haunting memory of my ghostly ghost pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does he do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back on the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still a mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些人真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those guys are dorks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  不过是我的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but they're my dorks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.21,0:10:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得飞天魔鬼干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you think the Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我们在卧铺里等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,asked us to wait in our bunk room?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是他要给我们奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's going to give us a reward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说电影票吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like movie passes?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者是超大咖啡杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or an oversized coffee mug
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop bouncing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们一辈子当我船员好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This whole "crew for eternity" thing isn't working out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与其说是你们的问题  不如说是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not really you, so much as it is me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要放了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're setting us free?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  我要吃掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, I'm just going to eat you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晩餐见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.44,0:11:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:11:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's leave
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the door is locked
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一的出路是穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the only way out is through the
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香水商店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perfume department
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么干了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌从那走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always hate going in there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.07,0:12:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear Diary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟他们讲我明天要吃掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've told them I'm going to eat them tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了那种棕酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l made up some of that brown sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前我表哥临时给我看过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my cousin showed me just for the occasion
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又找着我的饭点袜了  可真是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I found my dining sock again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得我上次丢了饭点袜不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember the last time I lost me dining sock?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当时我一整个星期都吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't eat for a whole week
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  有时我在想要是碰巧出了事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, sometimes I wonder how I survive
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还怎么好好过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anything should ever happen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我袜子还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my sock
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都清楚我没袜子吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows I can't eat without it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.41,0:13:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会把弹性拉没的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're stretching out the elastic
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像陷入僵局了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would seem we have reached an impasse
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉家伙说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink one is right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.83,0:13:34.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:34.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把袜子还我  我就给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you give me back the sock and I'll give you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要五个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it five
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要就拉倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it or leave it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有三个愿望  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three wishes, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishes?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能早点知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish we had known that earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你们就剩下两个愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got two wishes left
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦  还有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we still have two more
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望章鱼哥能来亲眼目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish Squidward were here to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm glad all that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼给了我们三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dutchman gave us three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星用了第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick used the first one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I guess I
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用掉了第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just used the second one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么最后一个是你们欠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then the last one you owe me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们又把我拖下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you got me back into this mess
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  愿望应该是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think it belongs to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.19,0:14:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我的神秘超凡力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Using my mystic otherworldly powers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我来决定最后一个愿望归谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall decide who gets the last wish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咿呢咪呢唛呢哞  抓住水手脚趾头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eenie-meenie-minie-mo, catch a sailor by the toe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果大叫放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he hollers, let him go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈教导我要挑最好的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mother told me to pick the very best one and
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快想  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, think, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're about to get eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以许什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can you wish for
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让我们不被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make it so we don't get eaten?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it all figured out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不会吃掉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won't be able to eat us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我希望飞天魔鬼是吃素的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I wish that the Dutchman was a vegetarian
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're home
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're safe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们为什么变水果了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why have we been turned into fruits?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也许了个愿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get a wish, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水果可以预防坏血病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And fruit prevents scurvy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here with that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逮着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, children
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.12,0:15:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们大家都非常喜欢刚刚的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope all you boys and girls enjoyed the show
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们现在必须走甲板落海身亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it's time for you to walk the plank
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I meant to say was
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来读粉丝来信了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for fan mail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  万众期待的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, the moment you've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好把牛奶从鼻子里喷出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So get ready to blow milk out your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们要拆信了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because we're going to open a letter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信封拿来  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The envelope please, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  我长羽毛的好助理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, my fine feathered assistant
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着你谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  闻到什么了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, you smell something?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脑袋装了引信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fuse in your head
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说过不耍特技了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, we're not doing that stunt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没收到备忘录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the memo
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.40,0:16:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯精选到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it for Patchy's Pick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.19,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(315,392)}给小蜗洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.67\pos(294,372)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:53.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.67\pos(422,694)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.1\pos(406,272)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.1\pos(310,348)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.1\pos(472,668)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  又到了每周必经的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, looks like it's that time of week again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗澡时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bath time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  去把水准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go get the water started
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要让你进浴缸里去  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to get in that tub, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我可以给你来硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Gary, we can do this the hard way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以来软的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or the easy way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以来软硬适中的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or the medium way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以来半适中软硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or the semi-medium, easy-hard way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以来硬中带软外加软硬皆施的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or the sort of hard with a touch of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,awkward-easy difficult-challenging way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你非要这么玩是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's how you want to play it, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  来看这个新玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, check out this new toy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fetch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新回旋宠物球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New boomerang pet ball
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really works
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我胸口绑了一颗炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a bomb strapped to my chest
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不去洗澡  三秒就会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna explode in three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unless you take a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.55,0:18:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要用潜意识信息侵入你的心智
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am now going to assault your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with subliminal messages
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,522)}肥皂
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你看到那种画面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry you had to see that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  法式贵族餐厅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, fancy French restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.83,0:18:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边有只不洗澡的淘气蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a naughty snail here who won't take a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再说一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you say that again?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow down
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你讲话就跟说外语似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like you're speaking some other language
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gare
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来跳山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout some leap frog?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're turn
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.22,0:18:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gare
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来跳山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout some leap frog?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有张崭新干净的一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a crisp dollar bill
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要送给家里洗澡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the next fella to take a bath in this house
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样也没用是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That didn't work either, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我找到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what I found
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是张古老海盗藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an old pirate treasure map
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写着家里埋海盗宝藏的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,revealing the location of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buried pirate treasure in this very house
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(826,726)}不是浴室\N埋藏的宝藏
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去寻宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go get that treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向左四十步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now 40 paces to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.20,0:19:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,four
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,five
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,six
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seven
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.10,0:19:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eight
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ten
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.00,0:19:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十一
