Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,25
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,26
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,26
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,27
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,27
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,40
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,40
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝藏一定就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The treasure must be in here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.13,0:19:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, look
