Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate treasure chest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, no, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't the bathtub
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.12,0:19:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金币
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doubloons
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1082,584)}肥皂
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't drop 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这枚胸针
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this brooch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道蜗牛要胸针干什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what a snail would want with a brooch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快进浴缸里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you just get in the tub?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进浴缸里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the tub
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进浴缸里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the tub
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the tub
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你要么给我进浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Gary, are you going to get in this tub
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么我就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or am I gonna have to--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.35,0:20:33.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:33.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you, uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你再也骗不到我  也阻挠不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have duped and/or frustrated me for the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我没办法让你来洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if I can't get you to come to the bath
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能让澡来洗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to bring the bath to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,756)}蜗牛笑话
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗澡快递
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bath delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你分享
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have something to share with you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在等水啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water you waiting for, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在树上下不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stuck in a tree?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.30,0:21:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要让你洗心革面了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to clean up your act, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把小蜗洗过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bathed Gary too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把小蜗皮洗没了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and removed his skin
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上把梯子放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring that ladder back this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am really not amused, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定得洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are going to take a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且一定得马上洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you are going to get clean right now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.36,0:22:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是你的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so the boss of you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里也许是个自由的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It may be a free country
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你住我家  就必须按我的规矩办事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you live in my house, under my rules
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许对我用那样的口气说话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't use that tone of voice with me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说什么你就得做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will do what I say, when I say
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.35,0:22:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.65,0:22:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说话呢  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am talking to you, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准靠近那个泥坑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do not go near that mud puddle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛小蜗  你听没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary the Snail, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你三秒钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am giving you three seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你离泥坑远点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get away from that mud puddle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.73,0:22:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.03,0:22:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.42,0:22:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二点五
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two and a half
